It came with some gold.

32:09.093 --> 32:10.762
My name is Jung Gicheul.

33:24.836 --> 33:27.213
SEOUL CENTRAL PROSECUTOR'S AUTHORITY

33:30.216 --> 33:31.217
Hello.

33:35.346 --> 33:38.933
I'm Murayama Hideaki. Tokyo Police,
Narcotics Control Division.

33:41.269 --> 33:44.355
Cho Changsik, Chief Prosecutor,
Serious Crime Division.

33:48.234 --> 33:50.278
- I am pleased.
- You too.

33:50.361 --> 33:53.156
When I said the drugs were too expensive,

33:55.658 --> 33:57.410
said the drug dealer

33:58.911 --> 34:00.038
that he gets the drugs

34:00.955 --> 34:04.459
fra yakuzaerne i Yoshioka-gumi,

34:04.542 --> 34:06.294
so he couldn't make it cheaper.

34:07.962 --> 34:12.300
Because the premium quality product
with 99% purity

34:12.717 --> 34:14.552
is imported from Korea.

34:15.803 --> 34:17.722
But just calm down.

34:18.473 --> 34:20.850
They say we are going to get

34:20.933 --> 34:23.186
over 10 kg every month from Korea.

34:23.311 --> 34:26.147
- "Over 10 kg every month from Korea."
- Of course it will

34:27.523 --> 34:29.609
result in a price drop.

34:29.692 --> 34:31.819
"This will naturally
result in a price drop."

34:33.821 --> 34:35.073
We let that drug dealer go

34:35.156 --> 34:37.241
in return for these statements,

34:37.325 --> 34:39.202
but he was murdered three days ago.

34:39.285 --> 34:42.288
We suspect it was revenge
from those in Yoshioka-gumi.

34:45.374 --> 34:47.418
Drug trade with Japan.

34:49.754 --> 34:52.006
It's probably a Korean gang.

34:54.133 --> 34:55.760
Getting the Korean Amphetamine Cook

34:55.843 --> 34:59.222
and the smuggler arrested is not enough.

34:59.305 --> 35:02.308
There are many
Yoshioka-gumi members throughout Japan.

35:02.391 --> 35:05.228
We must find out
which member in which part and region,

35:05.311 --> 35:07.063
that imports and distributes amf.

35:07.146 --> 35:08.981
And to ensure hard evidence,

35:09.315 --> 35:12.360
may we catch the smugglers in the act.

35:13.986 --> 35:15.113
Captured.

35:15.279 --> 35:17.740
Do you have someone who fits this case?

35:17.824 --> 35:19.033
EUMSEONG, SOUTH KOREA

35:19.117 --> 35:20.785
One who is tenacious.

35:20.868 --> 35:22.328
Which does not stick out.

35:22.787 --> 35:25.248
I know a guy.

35:26.124 --> 35:27.291
He's a little wild,

35:27.792 --> 35:28.751
men...

35:29.168 --> 35:30.628
He is perfect for the job.

35:33.214 --> 35:34.215
Your asshole.

35:35.299 --> 35:36.300
Let go of me!

35:37.844 --> 35:39.595
Don't interfere.

35:57.572 --> 35:58.698
So refreshing.

36:04.203 --> 36:05.955
Don't want to go to Seoul?

36:06.205 --> 36:08.249
I come home a few times a month.

36:09.500 --> 36:10.710
That was not what I meant.

36:13.087 --> 36:15.756
Do you want to do something new in Seoul?

36:19.719 --> 36:22.180
Something you haven't done before.
Something a little dangerous.

36:25.558 --> 36:27.059
So that's why you're here.

36:27.560 --> 36:28.728
You will never come here.

36:32.857 --> 36:34.609
You must infiltrate their group,

36:34.692 --> 36:38.404
and if you see, hear about,
and participate in amphetamine trafficking,

36:38.487 --> 36:40.698
then we can also catch the Japanese.

36:41.574 --> 36:44.619
So I have to be a dirty guy
to catch the dirty guys.

36:44.702 --> 36:45.661
Preach

36:46.871 --> 36:50.166
Have you ever
researched this way before?

36:56.172 --> 36:57.757
Come now.

36:57.840 --> 37:00.218
If you want to catch thugs,

37:00.301 --> 37:03.054
then you track them.
You don't become one of them.

37:05.139 --> 37:07.934
Come on, we're cops.
It is degrading.

37:08.684 --> 37:11.520
And when my wife's family hears about it,

37:11.604 --> 37:13.689
they will say I do crazy things

37:14.649 --> 37:17.026
instead of studying
for the promotion exam.

37:18.653 --> 37:22.448
Amphetamine in the billions, enough to
make 330,000 people affected,

37:22.531 --> 37:24.450
must spread across the country.

37:24.867 --> 37:26.077
Think of your father.

37:33.334 --> 37:36.254
When you hate something so much,
you can't even look at it.

37:40.091 --> 37:42.218
Forget it. I will not do it.

37:42.468 --> 37:45.930
There are many other officers
who can do that.

37:56.565 --> 37:57.775
How can I help?

37:57.900 --> 38:00.278
Is Officer Park Junmo here?

38:00.361 --> 38:01.862
Junmo.

38:05.992 --> 38:07.368
He's over there.

38:07.868 --> 38:08.703
What is it?

38:11.205 --> 38:16.085
I heard you and NCID's
Captain Seok Dohyung are like brothers.

38:16.168 --> 38:19.839
A difficult high school student from Daejeon
who was known for fighting.

38:20.464 --> 38:24.135
And a friendly police officer
who steered him in the right direction.

38:24.218 --> 38:25.636
I asked Captain Seok

38:25.720 --> 38:29.682
to recommend someone
suitable for this investigation,

38:30.224 --> 38:31.851
and he said your name right away.

38:31.934 --> 38:34.437
But I have said no.

38:36.105 --> 38:38.149
All the police chiefs

38:38.232 --> 38:41.402
obviously knows about
the incidents at your wedding.

38:42.945 --> 38:46.949
Even I wouldn't give a promotion

38:47.033 --> 38:48.826
to the son of a drug addict.

39:02.965 --> 39:04.800
If this case ends well,

39:04.884 --> 39:07.470
you get a significant bonus
and a special promotion.

39:08.804 --> 39:10.931
You can't stay
in the low ranks forever.

39:14.185 --> 39:15.895
Attendant Park,

39:15.978 --> 39:19.523
chances like this don't come around every day.

39:20.775 --> 39:22.610
You can rise through the ranks

39:23.486 --> 39:25.404
with the help of the prosecution.

39:27.990 --> 39:29.950
Your wife has been selected for Seoul

39:30.034 --> 39:32.161
with his promotion to police assistant.

39:32.828 --> 39:33.829
Isn't that wonderful?

39:52.556 --> 39:54.058
SOUTHERN SEOUL PLAZA

41:01.125 --> 41:02.126
Come now.

41:26.275 --> 41:27.693
I do so on one condition.

41:27.776 --> 41:28.694
A condition?

41:28.986 --> 41:30.154
Forget the bonus.

41:33.115 --> 41:35.409
But I want to move up two rows.

41:39.079 --> 41:40.664
- Two rows?
- Yes.

41:42.416 --> 41:46.253
I'm the only one
who puts life on the line.

41:47.546 --> 41:49.423
I think I deserve it.

41:52.426 --> 41:54.595
If it ends well,

41:54.678 --> 41:56.680
Aren't you also rising in the ranks?

41:57.765 --> 41:58.891
Why...

42:00.851 --> 42:05.397
...don't you ascend
with the help of a subordinate officer?

42:13.447 --> 42:14.823
Is there any precedent?

42:14.907 --> 42:16.784
In 1989 to capture Im Jongseok.

42:16.867 --> 42:19.995
The head of the Students' National Council.

42:28.295 --> 42:29.296
Okay.

42:41.058 --> 42:43.477
Recently, amphetamine
with over 95% purity

42:43.561 --> 42:47.106
been widespread in Gangnam as in Japan.

42:47.189 --> 42:48.899
Specifically, Gangnam Crystal.

42:48.983 --> 42:51.694
We thought
it was connected to gangsters in Gangnam,

42:51.777 --> 42:53.862
so we did a little digging.

42:53.946 --> 42:54.989
Before was Jang Kyungchul,

42:55.072 --> 42:57.950
also known as "Sergeant Jang",
commander of the area.

42:58.033 --> 42:59.702
But Jung Gicheul overthrew him,

42:59.785 --> 43:02.329
which Busan's Song Donghyuk disregarded.

43:02.413 --> 43:05.165
Jung Gicheul is now the leader of Gangnam Union,

43:05.249 --> 43:08.627
and the main members of the new
gang are students from Yeoksam High School.

43:09.128 --> 43:11.797
They have been like brothers
since they were very young,

43:11.880 --> 43:13.632
so they have a bond like a family.

43:13.716 --> 43:16.802
Therefore, we did not rely on our
usual investigative methods,

43:16.927 --> 43:19.388
and so we planned this.

43:20.514 --> 43:22.308
When Jung wanted to get rid of Jang,

43:22.391 --> 43:24.310
a member was stabbed to death.

43:24.602 --> 43:25.853
His name was Kwon Taeho.

43:25.936 --> 43:28.564
He was Jung Gicheul's
best friend from high school.

43:29.398 --> 43:32.693
The members of Gangnam Union said
that Sergeant Jang was the killer,

43:32.776 --> 43:35.946
but since he disappeared,
the case has never been solved.

43:37.156 --> 43:38.157
Gangnam Union...

43:38.699 --> 43:41.243
Is there anything else special about them?

43:41.327 --> 43:43.996
Gangnam Union took power
in Gangnam really fast.

43:46.457 --> 43:47.458
From the outside

43:47.541 --> 43:50.919
it almost looks like a social club
for young entrepreneurs.

43:52.254 --> 43:55.883
But over
the past six months in Gangnam

43:55.966 --> 43:58.385
they have almost taken over all the nightclubs.

43:59.345 --> 44:00.971
Where did they get all that money from?

44:01.055 --> 44:02.514
KARAOKE, LUCKY DISCO

44:02.598 --> 44:05.267
It probably has
something to do with Gangnam Crystal.

44:06.727 --> 44:09.647
Junmo, you will now be
Kwon Taeho's fake cousin

44:09.730 --> 44:11.857
of the same age named Kwon Seungho,

44:11.940 --> 44:13.734
and you need to be close to Gangnam Union.

44:13.817 --> 44:16.695
This is the backstory
we made up for Kwon Seungho.

44:16.779 --> 44:18.739
He works as a fisherman.

44:19.156 --> 44:20.115
Kwon Seungho.

44:20.199 --> 44:23.077
I'll take care of
his backstory beforehand.

44:23.160 --> 44:24.161
Do not think about it.

44:24.244 --> 44:26.246
Do you know Sikgaek in Yeoksam-dong?

44:26.914 --> 44:29.583
They recently took over that business.

44:30.042 --> 44:33.003
Some of the members
eat dinner there several times a week,

44:33.087 --> 44:34.963
and we suppose they are high-ranking.

44:35.881 --> 44:38.342
Safety is key
to the success of this operation.

44:38.425 --> 44:41.553
There may be cops
who are close to the gangsters,

44:41.637 --> 44:43.722
so let's be discreet from the start.

44:43.806 --> 44:44.723
Hello.

44:46.058 --> 44:48.644
Do you take sick leave when you look so healthy?

44:50.396 --> 44:51.271
Junmo.

44:52.022 --> 44:52.981
Are you okay?

44:53.065 --> 44:53.982
Hello.

44:55.526 --> 44:57.361
- Take care of yourself, okay?
- Okay.

44:57.444 --> 44:58.904
Get well.

44:58.987 --> 45:00.030
Asthma?

45:01.865 --> 45:04.201
Gangnam Unions chef, Jung Gicheul.

45:06.662 --> 45:08.539
According to his travel records,

45:08.622 --> 45:10.290
within the last six months,

45:10.374 --> 45:12.543
he has visited Japan and China twice.

45:15.587 --> 45:16.588
Depth?

45:17.131 --> 45:19.800
If they manufacture Gangnam Crystal themselves,

45:19.883 --> 45:23.971
then maybe they buy the
ingredient ephedrine in China.

45:25.848 --> 45:27.850
Gangnam Union and Jung Gicheul.

45:29.435 --> 45:32.396
The worst drug crime
in Korean history.

45:36.108 --> 45:37.234
Now let's think about,

45:38.193 --> 45:40.237
how Kwon Seongho should

45:40.320 --> 45:42.656
go to Jung Gicheul first time.

45:44.283 --> 45:45.826
Let me try my way.

45:49.538 --> 45:51.498
GANGNAM UNION
JUNG GICHEUL

