46:40.464 --> 46:42.591
I am the owner.
I don't know what you mean.

46:44.009 --> 46:46.804
I know
Gangnam Union took over this place.

46:46.887 --> 46:48.597
Isn't Jung Gicheul the owner?

46:49.097 --> 46:50.474
Get me Jung Gicheul.

46:51.975 --> 46:52.976
Hurry up.

46:53.560 --> 46:54.561
He's over there.

46:59.066 --> 47:00.067
Who are you?

47:00.567 --> 47:03.237
We have customers, so get up and go.

47:05.155 --> 47:08.242
If I get up,
you'll end up on the floor, you rats.

47:09.284 --> 47:11.703
Now just get me Jung Gicheul.

47:12.538 --> 47:13.664
What?

47:14.998 --> 47:17.167
Damn it. Fine.

47:19.169 --> 47:20.254
You fucking...

47:24.883 --> 47:25.717
Before hell.

47:28.053 --> 47:31.682
Boss, shouldn't we eat
somewhere other than Sikgaek today?

47:31.765 --> 47:33.058
Why?

47:33.433 --> 47:35.477
Download Jung Gicheul.

47:35.811 --> 47:37.396
Get the owner.

47:38.313 --> 47:39.648
Can you hear me?

47:39.731 --> 47:41.483
Then get Jung Gicheul.

47:41.692 --> 47:44.278
There is obviously a madman
in the making.

47:44.361 --> 47:47.030
I'll take care of it after dinner.

47:48.282 --> 47:49.241
Who is he?

47:49.324 --> 47:53.370
SIKGAEK

47:57.833 --> 47:59.501
No, stop!

47:59.585 --> 48:00.878
Don't throw it away.

48:02.588 --> 48:04.256
He wants to talk to Gicheul.

48:05.757 --> 48:06.884
Me?

48:06.967 --> 48:08.010
Yes, boss.

48:08.468 --> 48:09.553
Why?

48:09.636 --> 48:11.597
Those kinds of guys never say why.

48:11.680 --> 48:12.764
Just forget it.

48:14.224 --> 48:15.809
Who the hell is that?

48:19.730 --> 48:20.981
Fucking idiots.

48:21.607 --> 48:22.858
Get the boss.

48:29.031 --> 48:30.115
Let's examine it.

48:31.199 --> 48:33.535
Crazy people need a lesson.

48:36.330 --> 48:38.040
Get Jung Gicheul!

48:44.212 --> 48:45.505
Come on.

49:18.914 --> 49:20.540
